{"tid":1767194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那外交部：暫停美軍艦機訪港    美海軍：或在台灣總統大選前後入港高雄","createTime":"2019-12-03T06:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T08:58:32.000Z","uid":79563,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"aebc3ba8c87545a73368b5504a9e38070d109f6e","tid":1767194,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:34:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2582124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2582124&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0Ksc4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=c9851bf2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2582124&h=9d67b5c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2582124</a><br />\n<br />\n敏感時機！美海軍船艦停泊進高雄港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2018/10/16/phpqcLStH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2018%2F10%2F16%2FphpqcLStH.jpg&h=4bca58e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國海軍研究辦公室（Office of Naval Research）科學研究船湯瑪斯號。（記者洪定宏攝）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔記者涂鉅旻／台北報導〕美國海軍研究辦公室（Office of Naval Research）排水量3250噸的科學研究船湯瑪斯號（Thomas G. Thompson （T-AGOR-23）），現正停靠於高雄港9號碼頭，前海軍新江艦長呂禮詩稍早在個人臉書揭露此訊息，他受訪時表示，該艦下個目的地為澳洲弗里曼特爾（Fremantle）港，如途中須整補，也可南下至菲律賓，卻選擇在高雄港停泊，其象徵意義值得觀察。<br />\n<br />\n呂禮詩的臉書揭露此訊息表示，該艦由美國大學暨國家海洋實驗室（University-National Oceanographic Laboratory System, UNOLS）使用，並具遙控水下載具（Remotely Operated Vehicle, ROV）及自主式水下載具（autonomous underwater vehicle, AUV），可測量鹽度，溫度，壓力和化學性質等水文資料。預計在本月18日晚間11時離港，前往澳洲弗里曼特爾（Fremantle）港；這種廣義的美艦在這個敏感時間來台，引發了無限的想像空間。<br />\n<br />\n呂禮詩受訪時分析，雖單純就該艦停泊而言，本身意義並不算特殊，但在此時間來，有許多遐想空間，首先，美軍航艦可能在下月於東亞一帶活動的傳聞傳出後，高雄港外海為我國軍時常演習的「反潛第六區」，平均水深約500公尺，最深約1千公尺左右，為反潛操演適合地點，假如美國航艦有意自台海通過，也可能在現有資料基礎上，進一步確認水下水文。<br />\n<br />\n呂禮詩也說，該地同時也是1996年台海飛彈危機時，中國其中一枚東風15飛彈的彈落點，綜合這些因素，其實有很多意涵值得觀察。<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍研究辦公室為隸屬於美國海軍的科研單位，司職美國軍方、科研與學術單位、各種組織的統合工作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2018/10/16/phpf9h315.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2018%2F10%2F16%2Fphpf9h315.jpg&h=10007024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2018/10/16/phpbeRYWR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2018%2F10%2F16%2FphpbeRYWR.jpg&h=109fdb92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2018/10/16/phpcUwnEb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2018%2F10%2F16%2FphpcUwnEb.jpg&h=a33fb74d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9320c1c4ae819695244f3ad3dc94192ba87d5a56","tid":1767194,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:34:50.000Z","msg":"支那暫停美軍艦機訪港呢招, 應該嚇死美軍了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6155f46ca14e762ec61a5a8b261a864d2172aa","tid":1767194,"uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:35:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>環球時報以社評表示，雖然被制裁的美國國家民主基金會是非政府組織，但都與美國官方有緊密聯繫；暫停美軍艦機訪港，會讓美軍感到不方便，「但請自己去找美國國會和白宮說理」。這次採取的制裁措施只是最輕的，如果美方繼續升級在香港的挑釁，中方將會採取進一步的後續行動，強調「這只是中方第一波反制」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/um735Gv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fum735Gv.gif&h=94501fab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fca31a28a20f58ad2b2d2cc96b851a438357d74e","tid":1767194,"uid":92188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:35:52.000Z","msg":"捉蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9337e51bc58785ac096b426045c75f35120946","tid":1767194,"uid":259813,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:36:43.000Z","msg":"美帝識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"